snippet.title: ADOPTING PALISMEN?!? - The Owl House Season 2 Episode 6 Reaction - Zamber Reacts
snippet.description:
Cute animals... it's a win win


The Owl House S2 E6 - " Hunting Palismen "
Summary: It's Palisman Pairing Day at Hexside; Luz doesn't match with a Palisman of her own and soon she finds herself on an unexpected journey with a foe.


Support the official release of The Owl House on Disney+ and Disney Now.


What is "The Owl House"?
- The Owl House follows Luz, a self-assured teenage girl who accidentally stumbles upon a portal to a magical world where she befriends a rebellious witch, Eda, and an adorably tiny warrior, King. Despite not having magical abilities, Luz pursues her dream of becoming a witch by serving as Eda's apprentice at the Owl House and ultimately finds a new family in an unlikely setting.
